    "We discuss our ongoing work and future research directions.",
    "We hope our work will inspire the design, research, and development of social interfaces that make LLMs easy and enjoyable to use.Fig. 2:2Fig.",
    "2: With Wordflow, users can easily manage and customize their prompts.",
    "(A) The Personal Prompt Library provides an overview of local prompts, allowing users to search, sort, and customize the quick-action prompt toolbar in the Editor View.",
    "(B) The Prompt Editor, activated by clicking a Prompt Card, employs progressive disclosure to help users edit basic prompt information, advanced settings (e.g., output parsing rules and LLM temperature), and sharing configurations."
